dcterms:description: Measurement data gathered from Phasor Measurement Units (PMUs) installed in the power system network for determining the approximate linear model. The data includes rotor angles of generators during transient events to capture the overall dynamics of the system.
dcterms:title: Measurement data from Phasor Measurement Units (PMUs)
